<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang = "vi">
<head>
	<meta charset ="UTF-8"/>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>Hoctot.vn</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
		<div id="header">
			<header class="container-fluid">
				
				<div id = "logo">
					<a class="navbar-brand" href="#" onclick="home()">
					<script> 
						function home(){
							window.location.assign('/')
						}
					</script>
						<img src="/hoctot.png" alt="" style="auto">
					</a>
				</div>

				
				<ul class="nav nav-pills pull-right">
					
					<li class="dropdown">
					<a href="#" onclick="signin()" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Đăng nhập<span class="caret"></span></a>
					<script> 
						function signin(){
							window.location.assign('/signin')
						}
					</script>
					</ul>
				</li>
				</ul>
				
				<div class="container center_div">
					<form class="navbar-form" method="post" action="/">
						<input type="text" class="form-control" name="search" placeholder="Tìm kiếm tài liệu & đề thi...">
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></span></button>
					</form>
				</div>

			</header>
		</div>


		<!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
		<div class="navbar-header">
			<button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1" aria-expanded="false">
				<span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
				<span class="icon-bar"></span>
				<span class="icon-bar"></span>
				<span class="icon-bar"></span>
			</button>
		</div>
		<!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
		<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
			<ul class="nav navbar-nav">
				<li><a href="/"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span> Trang chủ </a></li>
				<li><a href="/toan">Toán Học</a></li>
				<li><a href="/van">Ngữ Văn</a></li>
				<li class="dropdown">
					<a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Ngoại Ngữ <span class="caret"></span></a>
					<ul class="dropdown-menu">
						<li><a href="/eng">English</a></li>
						<li><a href="/phap">French</a></li>
						<li><a href="/nhat">Japanese</a></li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li class="dropdown">
					<a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Khoa học Tự Nhiên<span class="caret"></span></a>
					<ul class="dropdown-menu">
						<li><a href="/ly">Vật Lý</a></li>
						<li><a href="/hoa">Hóa Học</a></li>
						<li><a href="/sinh">Sinh Học</a></li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li class="dropdown">
					<a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Khoa học Xã hội<span class="caret"></span></a>
					<ul class="dropdown-menu">
						<li><a href="/su">Lịch Sử</a></li>
						<li><a href="/dia">Địa Lý</a></li>
						<li><a href="/gdcd">Công Dân</a></li>		
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li><a href="#">Video</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div><!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
	</nav>


	<div role="main" id="main">
		<div class="container-fluid">
		<!-- Add Carousel -->
		<section>
			<div id = "banner" class="row">
				<div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
					<!-- Indicators -->
					<ol class="carousel-indicators">
						<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
						<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1"></li>
						<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2"></li>
					</ol>

					<!-- Wrapper for slides -->
					<div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
						<div class="item active">
							<img src="bgr1.png" alt="">
							<div class="carousel-caption">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="item">
							<img src="bgr2.jpg" alt="">
							<div class="carousel-caption">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="item">
							<img src="bgr3.png" alt="">
							<div class="carousel-caption">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Controls -->
					<a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" role="button" data-slide="prev">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
					</a>
					<a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" role="button" data-slide="next">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
					</a>
				</div>			
			</div>
		</section>
				
				<section> 
					<div class = "row">
						<div class = "col-md-12">
							<h3><u> Đề thi mới:</u></h3>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
				
				<section> 
					<div class="container">
						<div class="row">
						<% results.forEach(function(result) { %>
							<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
								<a href="/giaodiendethi/<%=result.id%>" class="thumbnail">
									
									<img src="<%=result.link%>" alt="de1" style="width:150px;height:150px">
								</a>
								<p style="text-align:center"><%=result.name%></p> 
							</div>
						<% }); %>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
				
				<section> 
					<h3><u> Tin tức tuyển sinh 2019:</u></h3>

				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
					<a target="_blank" href="https://news.zing.vn/vi-sao-sinh-vien-duoc-nang-diem-thi-thpt-quoc-gia-khong-bi-duoi-hoc-post935490.html">
						<img src="tin1.jpg" alt="" width="auto" height="auto" class="center img-responsive">
					</a>
					<div class="desc">Vì sao SV được nâng điểm thi THPT quốc gia không bị đuổi học?</div>
				</div>	

				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
					<a target="_blank" href="https://news.zing.vn/thi-thpt-quoc-gia-co-thi-sinh-dang-ky-20-nguyen-vong-post937917.html">
						<img src="tin2.jpg" alt="" width="auto" height="auto" class="center img-responsive">
					</a>
					<div class="desc">Thi THPT quốc gia: Có thí sinh đăng ký 20 nguyện vọng</div>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
					<a target="_blank" href="https://news.zing.vn/bo-cong-an-se-co-quy-dinh-dac-thu-de-han-che-gian-lan-thi-cu-post936765.html">
						<img src="tin3.jpg" alt="" width="auto" height="auto" class="center img-responsive">
					</a>
					<div class="desc">Bộ Công an sẽ có quy định đặc thù để hạn chế gian lận thi cử</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
					<a target="_blank" href="https://tin.tuyensinh247.com/lich-thi-thpt-quoc-gia-nam-2019-chi-tiet-bo-gd-c24a41718.html">
						<img src="tin4.jpg" alt="" width="auto" height="auto" class="center img-responsive">
					</a>
					<div class="desc">Lịch thi THPT quốc gia 2019 - Chính thức từ Bộ Giáo dục</div>
				</div>		
				</section>
				
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


	<footer class ="bs-docs-footer">
		<div class="container">
			<ul>
				<p>Chia sẻ tài liệu ôn thi Đại học</p>
				<p>Design by Nhóm 8</p>
				<p> Chúc các bạn thi tốt!</p>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</footer>

</body>
</html>